Class MainController

  • java.lang.Object
    • Controller.MainController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class MainController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Main controller that links all pages, and sends information about parts/products Future Enhancement: This controller redundantly uses code to map forms. In the future, the system would benefit from a singular method for mapping forms. This would significantly save time the larger the project grows.
